h3 Carry a means of calling for help and keep it within reach.
p Should you end up in the water, unable to climb back onto your kayak, a buoyancy aid and the correct protective clothing (such as a drysuit) will buy you essential survival time. However, being able to call the Coastguard for help is essential for getting rescued and back to safety.
